Package: fflgis
Title: Freshwater Fisheries Laboratory library for manipulation of spatial data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(c("Colin", "P."), "Millar", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "C.Millar@marlab.ac.uk")
Description: A set of functions to help with the fitting of
    gmrf models in mgcv.  The package is intended for the fitting GMRF models
    such as random walks and seasonal effects.  The code is written as simply
    as possible to make is easy to see how GMRFs are constructed.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    sp,
    rgeos,
    rgdal,
    raster,
    maptools,
    deldir,
    igraph,
    dismo
Suggests:
    knitr (>= 1.8)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0
